candidate_problem_record.raw_question_text:
根据几年来对生态系统中几个营养水平的降雨量和生物量的测量结果(如下图所示),若降雨量为120英寸,请推测主要消费者的生物量范围是多少?

\begin{tikzpicture}
\begin{axis}[
 xlabel=降雨量 (英寸),
 ylabel=生物量,
 xmin=0, xmax=140,
 ymin=0, ymax=250,
 xtick={0,20,...,140},
 ytick={0,50,...,250},
 legend pos=north west,
 ymajorgrids=true,
 grid style=dashed,
]

\addplot[
 color=blue,
 mark=square,
 ]
 coordinates {
 (20,200)(40,150)(60,100)(80,50)(100,25)(120,10)
 };
 \addlegendentry{生产者}

\addplot[
 color=red,
 mark=triangle,
 ]
 coordinates {
 (20,60)(40,120)(60,180)(80,240)(100,180)(120,150)
 };
 \addlegendentry{主要消费者}

\addplot[
 color=orange,
 mark=o,
 ]
 coordinates {
 (20,10)(40,20)(60,30)(80,40)(100,50)(120,45)
 };
 \addlegendentry{次级消费者}

\end{axis}
\end{tikzpicture}

A. 150-200
B. 60
C. 45 
D. 20

